name: P12
post_condition_text: I used the questions presented by AI to determine if I had made the correct choice. For example, when AI would question the simple carbohydrates contained within pizza, it reminded me that those types of carbs easily spike glucose levels in individuals with Type II Diabetes. In addition, when it mentioned fiber content, or healthy fats, I knew I had made the correct meal choice, as those are elements that a Type II Diabetic should have in their meals.
post_challenge: On a couple of the photos, I was unable to determine what the food item was. This made it slightly difficult to identify if it was a source of fat, protein, or carbohydrates. Aside from that, the rest was quite simple. I chose the meals that consisted of complex carbohydrates, with a mix of protein and healthy fats.
